Rémi Laurent https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/R%C3%A9mi_Laurent 0 Rémi Laurent (12 October 1957, Suresnes – 14 November 1989, Paris) was a French actor, best known for playing the son Laurent in La Cage aux Folles. He died from an HIV related illness in 1989. Rémi_Laurent ( 12_October_1957 , Suresnes – 14_November_1989 , Paris ) was a_French_actor , best_known for playing the_son Laurent in La_Cage_aux_Folles .
